<time_sig>S.M. (6.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<title>Ʋba nan ʋlhpisa ƲIT143</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba nan ʋlhpisa
 E haiyaklo kak osh,
 Nan ashʋchi pia hokʋt
 Pilbaiyʋsha hoke.

[V2]
 Nan ashʋchi weki
 E shaiyali hokʋt
 Pishno ak inli hokʋto
 E kancha he keyu.

[V3]
 Ilbʋshʋt, yaha̱yʋt
 Il achukmʋli ka,
 Il anukfihinli kia,
 Nanihma he keyu.

[V4]
 Chisʋs Okchalinchi,
 Issish holitopa,
 Ilʋppak osh nan ashʋchi
 Kashoho̱ffi hoke.

[V5]
 Iti 'taiyukhʋna
 Takalit illi hosh,
 Falʋmminchi̱t Chihowa ya̱
 Isht pi ona yoke.</lyrics>
<aka>Conviction of sin and pardon through Jesus Christ.</aka>
</song>